<div class="dark-bg--underlay" data-gsap-el="section-rounded">
    <section class="brs-top">
        <div class="wrap">
            <h2><span>Goals</span></h2>
            <div class="rows">
                <p>Develop a CMS template for online electrical store. Original products: design series of sockets and switches, defeaters, climate control. Target audiences are interior designers, electricians, construction teams and businesses of different size.</p>
                <p>Each brand will have its own website with its own palette. Schneider Electric and Jung were selected for the early stages.</p>
