    </div>
</section>

<section class="border-top">
    <div class="wrap">
        <h2><span>Configurator (Jung)</span></h2>
        <div class="solution-layout">
            <div class="solution-desc rows">
                <p>On the Jung website, you can try out different colour combinations and select the most suitable one across each device series.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="solution-image">
                {{ components.video('jung-config.mp4', 'jung-config-poster.jpg', true, 'bordered') }}
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="border-top">
    <div class="wrap">
        <h2><span>Product page</span></h2>
        <div class="solution-layout">
            <div class="solution-desc rows">
                <p>Apart from the price, the most important information for the customer is the availability of the product and its quantity. Sometimes the required goods may not be in stock, and in such cases, they need to be ordered separately from the manufacturer. However, we will promptly inform users of this. The page also includes frames for sockets and switches.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="solution-image">
                {% image ["src/content/", folder, "/sch_product.jpg"] | join, "bordered", "Schneider Russia - product page screenshot",  [995, 1493]  %}
