        <div class="solution-layout">
            <div class="solution-desc rows">
                <p>At the checkout stage, you can select a pickup city, preferred delivery method and payment method. Following this, the order will be forwarded to the in-house CRM and processed by the shop team.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="solution-image">
                <div class="media-bg-layer--dark-gray">

                    {% image ["src/content/", folder, "/cart_list.jpg"] | join, "", "Schneider Russia - cart screenshot",  [995, 1493]  %}

                    {% image ["src/content/", folder, "/checkout.jpg"] | join, "", "Schneider Russia - checkout",  [995]  %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="border-top">
