            <div class="solution-desc rows">
                <ul class="bulleted-list--custom" data-gsap-el="bulletedList">
                    <li>The sites were developed using an in-house CMS, including a special module to handle shop-related features. Front-end: HTML + Smarty template engine, CSS, JQuery + plugins. Back-end: PHP, CodeIgniter.</li>
                    <li>Easy to use even on small devices.</li>
                    <li>Clear structure and search engine optimization had a beneficial effect on organic traffic.</li>
                    <li>Since its launch in 2020, the stores have attracted a large number of active users. Thousands of orders have been shipped to all regions of Russia. The shop team processes dozens of orders every day. In addition, we have used the template we have created to launch a number of other sites for other brands. All the websites are still maintained by Evernet.</li>
